Package stocker.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChartAlarm
    Represents an alarm within a chart.
    ChartIndicator
    Represents a technical indicator for a chart.
    ChartIndicatorBollingerBands
    Provides the Bollinger Bands as a technical indicator for a chart.
    ChartIndicatorSMA
    Provides the Simple Moving Average as a technical indicator for a chart.
    ChartWatchItem
    Represents an item (a stock, for instance) which is meant to be drawn as a chart.
    WatchItem
    Represents a generic item to be watched within Stocker (a stock, a currency, a crypto currency).
    WatchlistItem
    Represents an item (a stock, for instance) which is meant to be monitored in a watchlist.
